1.0.name: wordpress/contact-form-7-map-field
1.0.description:
This plugin provides a new field to Contact Form 7: a map with a coordinates marker, letting the user mark a location. The marker coordinates (longitude & latitude) are than passed to the contact form.

in version 2.0 i've added geolocation, making the map and marker to be focused on the supposed user location.
